Basically we want only headers - the code was working fine without any Server Busy or memory error when we were fetching only headers. However the header does not contain fields like 'To','From','CC' and that is why we are fetching mime_content. Is there any way to (1) fetch headers fields (Return-Path, Authentication-Results, Received, Received-SPF etc) and 'To','From','CC' together in one call or to (2) fetch the mime_content without the payload/body? Such that we get the required header fields without hitting the rate limiting policies of the server. 

Code snippet below - 

